source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_00<tab>The Vath strongarm is in a frightful panic.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_00<tab>Le transporteur des Vathes semble paniqué.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_01<tab>The Vath strongarm was ambushed by Gnath and forced to abandon his wain. Though the cargo held within is of great value, he fears his attackers still lurk thereabouts, and he asks that you recover it in his stead. Search near the river west of Loth ast Gnath for the abandoned goods.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_01<tab>Le transporteur des Vathes vous a demandé de récupérer à tout prix <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8AD50202 /var> qu'il a perdue en abandonnant sa charrette. Cherchez <var 33 ((EObj)) 02F61E9A890202 /var> au Déclin d'Avalonia.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_02<tab>As expected, the Gnath were lying in ambush and waiting for someone to try to recover the Vath strongarm's property. You promptly dispatch the assailants and recover the cargo. Take it back to Loth ast Vath.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez trouvé la charrette et récupéré le précieux chargement.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_03<tab>The Vath strongarm's cargo included a special gift for a lady Vath he has had his eye on. He is elated that you have recovered it for him, and grateful that you have avenged the Gnath's attack on him.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez rapporté <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8AD50202 /var> au transporteur. Il semblait très inquiet de ce qui serait arrivé à sa réputation s'il avait définitivement perdu ce chargement.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the cargo to the Vath strongarm.

TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_000<tab>We were attacked by Gnath from the Onemind! We fled in a hurry. We left behind our wain. The wain is full of goods. We must recover those goods. <click> <click> The goods are very precious. Very, very precious.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_000<tab>Kssss... Un Fidèle m'a attaqué<var 1D /var>! Je me suis enfui et j'ai laissé ma charrette derrière moi... Il faut que je la récupère, ksss...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_001<tab>But the Gnath may still be waiting! <click> <click> Generous hunter, you are strong. Could you recover our goods for us? We were attacked at the riverside, west of Loth ast Gnath. Our wain should still be there. Please recover our precious goods for us.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_001<tab>Elle se trouve à l'ouest de Loth ast Gnath, près de la rivière, ksss... Pouvez-vous récupérer la cargaison qui s'y trouve<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_010<tab>Our wain should be near Loth ast Gnath. To the west of Loth ast Gnath.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_010<tab>J'ai laissé ma charrette à l'ouest de Loth ast Gnath, près de la rivière, ksss... Pouvez-vous récupérer la cargaison qui s'y trouve<var 1D /var>?

TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_020<tab>J'ai laissé ma charrette à l'ouest de Loth ast Gnath, près de la rivière, ksss... Pouvez-vous récupérer la cargaison qui s'y trouve<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_021<tab>Ah, yes. This is it─delicious algae! We collected it as a gift. A gift for a special Vath. We are fond of her. Very fond of her.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_021<tab>Ksss... C'est bien ça, merci<var 1D /var>! Je suis le transporteur des Vathes... Ma fierté est de transporter plus vite et plus efficacement que quiconque, ksss...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_022<tab>So the Gnath were indeed lying in wait? Treacherous Gnath... <click> <click> Thank you for slaying them. You have given us not just our algae. You have also given us our revenge.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ302_01794_CRUSTACEANSLOVERGNATH01794_000_022<tab>Si les autres savaient que j'ai perdu un chargement, je devrais changer mon nom en <var 1A 02 /var>Transperdeur des Vathes<var 1A 01 /var><var 1D /var>! Je suis content que nous ne partagions pas la même conscience, eux et moi, ksss...
